00:18:13,307 --> 00:18:15,059
Ya. Mungkin.

298
00:18:16,102 --> 00:18:18,104
Aku belum memahaminya.

299
00:18:18,688 --> 00:18:19,814
Kira-kira apa?

300
00:18:21,941 --> 00:18:23,067
Kita harus mencari

301
00:18:24,443 --> 00:18:25,653
arti pesan itu.

302
00:18:26,737 --> 00:18:28,656
Kukira aku tahu penyebabnya,

303
00:18:28,739 --> 00:18:30,366
